{"tid":54535,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"平安夜  47歲休班警涉酒駕被捕","createTime":"2016-12-25T15:30:59.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T16:38:53.000Z","uid":62257,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2274ceca8c927b314726db4c8c135753cd2c8719","tid":54535,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T15:30:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/803248/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F803248%2F&d=XUrsYqOM6maeyggfL9i%2BrX8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=7abc2a09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F803248%2F&h=ad950fdc\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/803248/</a><br />\n<br />\n即時新聞港聞<br />\n<br />\n選擇分類&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n休班警平安夜涉酒駕被捕　暫准保釋下月報到<br />\n<br />\n2016-12-25 18:38&nbsp;文字大小<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n1/1一名47歲休班警員涉酒後駕駛被捕。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n一名47歲休班警員昨晚平安夜涉嫌在元朗僑興路酒後駕駛被捕，目前已獲准保釋候查，須於明年1月下旬向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n事發在昨晚11時半左右，38歲姓胡男途人報案指，發現一架私家車在元朗僑興路木頭村不穩定行駛。案件原列為發現可疑人士處理。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場經初步調查，發現47歲姓胡男司機未能通過酒精呼氣測試，涉嫌酒後駕駛被捕。被捕司機為一名休假中的警務人員。其後已獲准保釋候查，須於明年1月下旬向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，警隊非常重視人員操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。"},{"pid":"9791744f6616e3c7ff6132b291d2ef295c033d28","tid":54535,"uid":6222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T15:33:46.000Z","msg":"知道係自己人唔係會放生嫁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840292f4c8571c2c44c8b0cd24846f2a5d66eb4f","tid":54535,"uid":144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T15:35:01.000Z","msg":"47歲(被捕)(笑)"},{"pid":"761220d36b57894566186cc4ffc8edbe5852907a","tid":54535,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T15:54:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a977f2c271b70549cae209b7e393e1ab52726382","tid":54535,"u